Begin Row: k3, insert needle into next stitch as if to knit and wrap yarn 3 times around the point of the needle, then knit the stitch carrying extra loops on needle*
Repeat: k7; insert needle into next stitch as if to knit and wrap yarn 3 times around the point of the needle, then knit the stitch carrying extra loops on needle;

Begin Row: k3, sl 1 wyib dropping extra loops*
Repeat: k7, sl 1 wyib dropping extra loops
k3, sl 1 wyif, k3; insert needle into next stitch as if to knit and wrap yarn 3 times around the point of the needle, then knit the stitch carrying extra loops on needle
k3, sl 1 wyib, k3, sl 1 wyib, dropping extra wraps
k3; insert needle into next stitch as if to knit and wrap yarn 3 times around the point of the needle, then knit the stitch carrying extra loops on needle; k3, sl 1 wyif
End Row: k3; insert needle into next stitch as if to knit and wrap yarn 3 times around the point of the needle, then knit the stitch carrying extra loops on needle; k3

Repeat: k3, sl 1 wyib, dropping extra wraps, k3, sl 1 wyib
End Row: k3, k3, sl 1 wyib, dropping extra wraps, k3
